{"tid":1817423,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"梁凱寧著長冷衫遮身材拍節目？透薄黑絲成功搶焦點！","createTime":"2020-01-09T05:29:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-09T05:52:41.000Z","uid":19552,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"08d02d1fddded88fba3d8f4232e5902c4e66b8ed","tid":1817423,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T05:29:05.000Z","msg":"梁凱寧 (Maggie)近日密密參與拍攝短片節目，她日前就在Instagram 分享最新工作，指自己正在參與有關教育的拍攝，她今次一改比較充滿專業主播感覺的連身裙、套裝，改為穿上一件樽領粉藍色冷衫，( 或許是故意遮掩身材？) 不過下身就是短褲 ( 還是短裙？)再加上十分透薄的黑色絲襪，打扮充滿少女味，又與早前Maggie 與一眾TVB前同事舉行聖誕Party的打扮甚為相似呢！<br />\n<br />\n正所謂「寶物尋歸底」，Maggie在帖文內的第一張相只拍攝至肩賻部份，而第二、三張相片才是受到不少網民關注的黑色絲襪，是故意令到大家心癢癢嗎？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images.weserv.nl/?url=upload%2Ecc%2Fi1%2F2020%2F01%2F08%2FGdR8r0%2Ejpg&amp;w=680&amp;output=jpg&amp;q=80&amp;we&amp;errorredirect=upload%2Ecc%2Fi1%2F2020%2F01%2F08%2FGdR8r0%2Ejpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.weserv.nl%2F%3Furl%3Dupload%252Ecc%252Fi1%252F2020%252F01%252F08%252FGdR8r0%252Ejpg%26w%3D680%26output%3Djpg%26q%3D80%26we%26errorredirect%3Dupload%252Ecc%252Fi1%252F2020%252F01%252F08%252FGdR8r0%252Ejpg&h=16b8a42f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n網民當然有對Maggie的打扮「心心眼」，但都令人說笑地表示Maggie所指的教育主題拍攝，是指性教育嗎？<br />\n<img src=\"https://images.weserv.nl/?url=upload%2Ecc%2Fi1%2F2020%2F01%2F08%2F9Acwi1%2Ejpg&amp;w=680&amp;output=jpg&amp;q=80&amp;we&amp;errorredirect=upload%2Ecc%2Fi1%2F2020%2F01%2F08%2F9Acwi1%2Ejpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.weserv.nl%2F%3Furl%3Dupload%252Ecc%252Fi1%252F2020%252F01%252F08%252F9Acwi1%252Ejpg%26w%3D680%26output%3Djpg%26q%3D80%26we%26errorredirect%3Dupload%252Ecc%252Fi1%252F2020%252F01%252F08%252F9Acwi1%252Ejpg&h=2da97350&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://images.weserv.nl/?url=upload%2Ecc%2Fi1%2F2020%2F01%2F08%2FCzw0Wd%2Ejpg&amp;w=680&amp;output=jpg&amp;q=80&amp;we&amp;errorredirect=upload%2Ecc%2Fi1%2F2020%2F01%2F08%2FCzw0Wd%2Ejpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.weserv.nl%2F%3Furl%3Dupload%252Ecc%252Fi1%252F2020%252F01%252F08%252FCzw0Wd%252Ejpg%26w%3D680%26output%3Djpg%26q%3D80%26we%26errorredirect%3Dupload%252Ecc%252Fi1%252F2020%252F01%252F08%252FCzw0Wd%252Ejpg&h=df4dfb98&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://images.weserv.nl/?url=upload%2Ecc%2Fi1%2F2020%2F01%2F08%2FmEuQZ2%2Ejpg&amp;w=680&amp;output=jpg&amp;q=80&amp;we&amp;errorredirect=upload%2Ecc%2Fi1%2F2020%2F01%2F08%2FmEuQZ2%2Ejpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.weserv.nl%2F%3Furl%3Dupload%252Ecc%252Fi1%252F2020%252F01%252F08%252FmEuQZ2%252Ejpg%26w%3D680%26output%3Djpg%26q%3D80%26we%26errorredirect%3Dupload%252Ecc%252Fi1%252F2020%252F01%252F08%252FmEuQZ2%252Ejpg&h=d5ccbd2c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不過，Maggie近日擔任節目主持又的確多了不同令人討好的打扮，不只是只單單在公仔箱內報導新聞，有幾多拍攝全身、「大頭」的機會，真的需要在打扮上多花心思呢！或許這也是她離開TVB後的一大好處吧！大家不單可在更多資訊性節目中看到Maggie的蹤影，更可以看到性感打扮......"},{"pid":"5e5fdd8b546cd2f9dba4cebf1757ca7f220c72f9","tid":1817423,"uid":1734,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T05:29:58.000Z","msg":"始終都係要行雞既路線"},{"pid":"33f32f298cb20df30f8a98c73a4fcac5e6449931","tid":1817423,"uid":163704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T05:30:36.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n[全港最大的Fact Check平台-非食店篇]集合超過400間各地區各行業的良心店<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1817378\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1817378</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e5543c3f1fa80da52e486b4d194b206cf6ab10e6","tid":1817423,"uid":19552,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T05:30:51.000Z","msg":"心心眼=<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5961b0c62b74ebdaf962f8a5366367f6022df43","tid":1817423,"uid":78046,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T05:31:55.000Z","msg":"成日睇做梁凱晴 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50e32f0eb466d7c612910c4b94201a2dcb69f96b","tid":1817423,"uid":44748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,